divs: Sighting Detailsmy friends and i have wittnessed several ufos over the central bucks county area over the past 2-3 weeks. We are not sure exactly what they are but they appear low in the sky, brighter than any star and do not move for hours until they dissapear. We have taken pictures and still cannot figure out what they are. It dissapears from night to night, doesnt twinkle, and when staring at it long enough the light takes on the shape of a cross. The pictures we took look nothing like what we saw in the sky, and show strange flight patterns.
